Class RutaController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.webServices.rutas.controllers.RutaController

  • @RestController
 @RequestMapping(value="rutas")
 @EnableGlobalMethodSecurity(prePostEnabled=true)
public class RutaController
extends java.lang.Object
